---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
const pageTitle = "Membership";
---

<Layout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <div class="container">
    <article>
      <p>
        Royal Park Ladies Club warmly welcomes golfers of all levels. We provide
        a friendly, supportive and inclusive environment for all members
        regardless of ability and age.
      </p>
      <p>
        <span class="intro">Membership benefits include:-</span>
        <ul>
          <li>
            18 hole and 9 hole competitions every Tuesday from February to
            November
          </li>
          <li>Team competitions, monthly medals and annual trophies</li>
          <li>
            Regular social activities, including morning tea on game day and
            occasional lunches
          </li>
          <li>Annual Golf Trip</li><li>Opportunity to play VGL pennant</li>
          <li>Book tee times online using OneGolf</li>
          <li>Score competitions using the MiScore App</li>
          <li>Obtain a GA handicap</li><li>
            Participate in Summer Golf during December and January
          </li>
        </ul>
      </p>
      <h2>Fees</h2>
      <p>
        Annual Fees are currently $100 and these are reviewed annually. A
        nominal $5 match fee provides funds for the RPLGC to donate to a chosen
        charity, and assists with additional expenses such as trophy purchases.
      </p>
      <p>
        Green fees are paid to the Pro Shop. Rates are listed in the Pro Shop
        and on the Royal Park Golf Club website. Various concessions and the
        option to purchase a yearly subscription are also available.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you have further questions about joining the RPLGC, please <a
          href="/contact/">CONTACT US.</a
        >
      </p>
      <h2>Membership Resources</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="../Application for Membership 2025.pdf" target="_blank">MEMBERSHIP APPLICATION FORM</a></li>
        <li><a href="../RPLGC Club Information.pdf" target="_blank">INFORMATION FOR NEW MEMBERS</a></li>
      </ul>
      <h2>Newsletters</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="../Golf GOSS Nov24-Jan 2025.pdf" target="_blank">Golf GOSS Nov 2024 - Jan 2025</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </div>
  <style lang="scss">
    h1 {
      text-align: center;
    }
    .intro {
      font-weight: bold !important;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
